Pulltaps Two-Step Waiters Corkscrew Graphite Finish
List.Description: This Pulltap's Two-Step Waiter's Corkscrew with a graphite finish is not only extremely beautiful, but feels strong and sturdy in the hand. Pulltap's unique hinged double-lever system helps lift the cork along a straight vertical line so there is no struggling sideways against the bottle neck. Opener also includes a serrated knife blade and contoured steel handle. This corkscrew is a wonderful gift for any wine lover.
